channel.title: Omg i need help! every1 who knows about servers look!
channel.description:
OK, ive had my server up for about a week now. I got it setup and everything. It was online, people were loggin on and everything. And this morning, i woke up, turned on my server, and it says its offline????? Ive had it online for a week or so now. And all the sudden, it is offline??? How???? Please help!
DONT SAY portforwarding is incorrect! Bcuz it is correct, or else people wudnt have been able to login! And my internet connection is just fine, i am aloud on the internet, and everything. And port 43594 has been opened for days now! Omg i dnt know wuts goin on!
